ence in the origins of the AFM1 and AFM2 phases, and their relations\nwith the high superconducting transitions in Fe-pnictides.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Aug 2019 09:11:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-11"}
