 LDP protocols. Our experimental evaluation of LATENT on convolutional\ndeep neural networks demonstrates excellent accuracy (e.g. 91%- 96%) with high\nmodel quality even under low privacy budgets (e.g. $\\varepsilon=0.5$).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Aug 2019 10:13:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Nov 2019 06:00:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 9 Nov 2019 07:21:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-12"}
