n which\nscenarios, making sure that automated decision tools are created by people from\ndiverse backgrounds, and understanding the historical and political factors\nthat disadvantage certain groups who are subjected to these tools.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Aug 2019 15:35:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-20"}
